### Show Process - Success (Super Admin)
# @name showProcess
GET {{base_url}}{{apiVersion}}/processes/1
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

### Show Process - Success (Admin)
# @name showProcessAdmin
GET {{base_url}}{{apiVersion}}/processes/1
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

### Show Process - Success (Secretary)
# @name showProcessSecretary
GET {{base_url}}{{apiVersion}}/processes/1
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

### Show Process - Without Authentication
# Should return 401 Unauthorized
GET {{base_url}}{{apiVersion}}/processes/1
Accept: application/json

### Show Process - Not Found (404)
# Should return 404 without JSON
GET {{base_url}}{{apiVersion}}/processes/99999
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

